            <p class="cookie-ingredients"><strong>Ingredients:</strong> Crushed Oreos, cream filling pieces, butter, caster sugar, plain flour, eggs, vanilla extract, baking soda</p>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="cookie-showcase-item">
          <div class="cookie-showcase-image">
            <img src="cookies/chocolate-mousse-cookie.png" alt="Chocolate Mousse Luxury" />
          </div>
          <div class="cookie-showcase-content">
            <h3>Chocolate Mousse Luxury</h3>
