          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="cookie-showcase-item alt">
          <div class="cookie-showcase-image">
            <img src="cookies/pecan-cookie.png" alt="Pecan Pie Paradise" />
          </div>
          <div class="cookie-showcase-content">
            <h3>Pecan Pie Paradise</h3>
            <p>Buttery dough loaded with toasted pecan pieces, reminiscent of your favorite slice of pecan pie.</p>
